text: Kochkin () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Pchegatlukayskoye Rural Settlement of Teuchezhsky District, the Republic of Adygea, Russia. The population was 10 as of 2018. There are 2 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Teuchezhsky District
title: Kochkin, Pchegatlukayskoye Rural Settlement, Teuchezhsky District, Republic of Adygea
